WEBVTT



00:00:29.039 --> 00:00:31.839
Guangcai, don't tie me up.

00:00:34.039 --> 00:00:38.219
Guangcai, I'm sorry.
Guangcai, let me go.

00:00:39.320 --> 00:00:40.299
Give me a hit.

00:00:41.500 --> 00:00:42.340
Guangcai.

00:00:42.859 --> 00:00:44.340
That scoundrel Huang Mantang,

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.560
I thought he was just useless.

00:00:48.240 --> 00:00:51.700
I never expected him to get hooked
on drugs these past few years.

00:00:52.960 --> 00:00:55.200
Alright, Guangcai. Don't worry.

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:59.020
Keeping Huang Mantang
locked up here is definitely safe.

00:01:09.640 --> 00:01:10.599
Dazhu, listen.

00:01:11.340 --> 00:01:15.200
The villa project can take time.
Halting for two years is no big deal.

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:17.952
The later it goes public,
the higher the value climbs.

00:01:18.260 --> 00:01:20.400
But the situation now
is Huang Mantang is back.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.700
He's an unstable factor.

00:01:24.340 --> 00:01:25.920
Before the police come to us,

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:29.420
we need to figure out what to do next.

00:01:48.260 --> 00:01:50.420
Who is it? Is that Lijun?

00:01:51.980 --> 00:01:52.700
Lijun.

00:01:54.040 --> 00:01:54.780
Guangcai?

00:01:55.180 --> 00:01:56.060
Dazhu?

00:01:56.780 --> 00:01:57.900
Dazhu.

00:01:59.140 --> 00:02:00.420
Are you going to kill me?

00:02:01.780 --> 00:02:04.680
Listen, I'm not entirely unprepared.

00:02:05.420 --> 00:02:07.480
If I don't show up for a month,

00:02:08.620 --> 00:02:10.560
I guarantee
not a single one of you will live.

00:02:13.840 --> 00:02:14.840
(One just died.)

00:02:16.360 --> 00:02:17.840
The police are making a big move now.

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:22.699
If we want to live safely
for the rest of our lives,

00:02:23.639 --> 00:02:25.020
we cannot act rashly again.

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:29.240
But keeping him tied up here
forever isn't a solution.

00:02:36.360 --> 00:02:37.699
Then we control him.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:41.740
Starting today, we cannot
let the police find Huang Mantang.

00:02:42.360 --> 00:02:43.300
To be safe,

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:45.520
everything about him

00:02:47.460 --> 00:02:48.400
has to be erased.

00:02:51.199 --> 00:02:52.928
Something happened
at the construction site.

00:02:56.699 --> 00:02:58.520
We can use that to get rid of him.

00:04:08.800 --> 00:04:11.872
=The Silent Rift=

00:04:12.410 --> 00:04:14.874
=Episode 12=
(Darkest Hour)

00:04:18.579 --> 00:04:20.180
(All officers on duty today,)

00:04:20.899 --> 00:04:23.519
(work with drug enforcement.
Be ready to go at any time.)

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:29.259
(Starting today, search urban areas
and villages, and entertainment venues.)

00:04:30.639 --> 00:04:35.660
(Focus especially on individuals
with drug-related criminal records.)

00:04:35.980 --> 00:04:38.220
(Leave no one out. Continue the search.)

00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.259
- (Yes!)
- (Yes!)

00:06:33.240 --> 00:06:34.319
Back then, when Du Ming

00:06:36.439 --> 00:06:38.480
left the police force, he asked me

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.879
if he was a good cop.

00:06:44.879 --> 00:06:46.800
I told him he would
always be a good cop.

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:51.560
At that time,

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:54.860
his doing business as a boss

00:06:55.879 --> 00:06:56.819
was all fake.

00:06:57.180 --> 00:07:00.379
I was the one who assigned him
to the drug enforcement line.

00:07:02.300 --> 00:07:04.560
This was all confidential,
so I couldn't tell you.

00:07:08.819 --> 00:07:10.379
One thing I regret most

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.060
is letting you meet him.

00:07:16.360 --> 00:07:18.120
He asked me more than once

00:07:19.180 --> 00:07:21.740
if he could help you.

00:07:23.180 --> 00:07:26.240
He saw you had been stuck in this case
for so many years.

00:07:27.300 --> 00:07:29.060
He didn't want to see you so exhausted.

00:07:31.300 --> 00:07:32.300
But I disagreed.

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:36.500
Because it was too dangerous.

00:07:37.620 --> 00:07:38.879
He had his mission to finish.

00:07:40.740 --> 00:07:43.879
Zhu Helai, by resolution
of the superior leadership,

00:07:46.379 --> 00:07:48.060
you'll face administrative sanctions.

00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:51.920
Prepare yourself mentally.

00:08:59.514 --> 00:09:03.805
(Public Telephone)

00:09:22.039 --> 00:09:23.220
See you later, buddy.

00:09:26.539 --> 00:09:27.120
Bye.

00:09:39.019 --> 00:09:42.159
Officer Zhu, you coming here
is wasting your talent.

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:44.840
See? Our cafeteria is pretty routine.

00:09:45.139 --> 00:09:47.279
Mainly to match
the frontline officers' schedules.

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:49.000
Here, take a look.

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:52.240
There's some prep work to do.

00:09:54.039 --> 00:09:56.440
Everyone, welcome Officer Zhu.

00:09:57.759 --> 00:09:59.320
- Welcome, Officer Zhu.
- Welcome, Officer Zhu.

00:10:01.500 --> 00:10:02.759
Officer Zhu, I'm leaving.

00:10:02.940 --> 00:10:03.500
Master.

00:10:07.580 --> 00:10:08.120
Master.

00:10:09.159 --> 00:10:10.840
Just bear with it here for a while.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:13.080
I'll apply to get you
transferred back soon.

00:10:13.639 --> 00:10:16.100
It's fine. I'm good here.
I won't cause trouble. Go ahead.

00:10:16.700 --> 00:10:18.100
Master, I'm your apprentice.

00:10:18.580 --> 00:10:19.259
I'm okay.

00:10:20.259 --> 00:10:20.980
This is fine.

00:11:00.986 --> 00:11:03.354
(Beiyan City People's Hospital,
Gynecology)

00:11:22.360 --> 00:11:23.872
If A is a positive number,

00:11:23.872 --> 00:11:27.720
on which side of the origin is
point A on the number axis?

00:11:28.279 --> 00:11:29.639
On the right.

00:11:29.639 --> 00:11:30.360
Correct.

00:11:30.639 --> 00:11:31.480
You're back.

00:11:32.100 --> 00:11:32.899
Dad.

00:11:34.399 --> 00:11:37.360
On which side of the origin is point -A?

00:11:38.279 --> 00:11:39.340
That would be on the left.

00:11:39.620 --> 00:11:42.019
The food is in the pot.
We just ate. It's still warm.

00:11:42.019 --> 00:11:43.019
Go serve yourself some.

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.759
Qianqian, do the problems.

00:11:47.899 --> 00:11:49.360
Do you expect me to get it for you?

00:11:50.100 --> 00:11:51.080
You're not eating?

00:11:53.600 --> 00:11:54.480
Wrote the answers?

00:11:55.019 --> 00:11:55.720
I'll fix it.

00:11:57.899 --> 00:11:59.220
Yes, write the units.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.580
- Okay.
- I wrote it.

00:12:01.139 --> 00:12:02.019
Go back to sleep.

00:12:02.019 --> 00:12:03.712
Go to bed early.
I'll check on you later.

00:12:04.360 --> 00:12:04.860
Okay.

00:12:05.080 --> 00:12:06.139
Don't stay up late.

00:12:06.620 --> 00:12:07.159
Good night.

00:12:07.259 --> 00:12:07.840
Good night.

00:12:18.980 --> 00:12:21.259
Zhu, I made goji berry tea for you.

00:12:21.460 --> 00:12:24.399
People say that drinking
this helps with sleep.

00:12:24.720 --> 00:12:25.580
Have some.

00:12:27.340 --> 00:12:28.980
I saw you at the hospital today.

00:12:37.639 --> 00:12:40.659
It's no big deal.
Menopause came a bit early.

00:12:41.399 --> 00:12:43.500
The doctor says this illness
isn't life-threatening.

00:12:44.580 --> 00:12:47.139
I just wanted to tell you a bit later.

00:12:47.139 --> 00:12:49.100
We won't have our own child, will we?

00:12:53.519 --> 00:12:55.779
Actually, I've considered
Qianqian as my own child.

00:12:56.600 --> 00:12:57.480
I haven't thought

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:00.399
about having another one.

00:13:03.980 --> 00:13:04.779
But,

00:13:07.080 --> 00:13:09.580
when the doctor told me

00:13:10.980 --> 00:13:12.899
I truly couldn't give birth anymore,

00:13:14.600 --> 00:13:15.519
I...

00:13:17.259 --> 00:13:17.960
I just...

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:20.360
I just felt a bit...

00:13:28.519 --> 00:13:30.639
I'm going to bed. Don't stay up late.

00:14:49.360 --> 00:14:51.580
Huifen, wash your hands and let's eat.

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.720
After the meal, let's go out for a walk.

00:14:54.639 --> 00:14:55.776
Qianqian, you're awake.

00:14:56.899 --> 00:14:59.480
Dad, why haven't you gone
to work yet? You'll be late.

00:14:59.720 --> 00:15:01.779
Yeah, aren't you going to work?

00:15:01.980 --> 00:15:03.720
Not today. I took the day off.

00:15:04.120 --> 00:15:04.980
Stay with you today.

00:15:04.980 --> 00:15:07.259
Come, sit down. Qianqian, sit.

00:15:09.379 --> 00:15:10.899
Come. Today,

00:15:11.220 --> 00:15:13.720
the three of us will
go out and watch a movie.

00:15:14.220 --> 00:15:17.220
After that, we'll have a meal
at a restaurant.

00:15:18.399 --> 00:15:20.639
Here, Qianqian,
your favorite steamed bun.

00:15:21.720 --> 00:15:22.899
Peel the egg yourself.

00:15:23.720 --> 00:15:26.139
Well, Huifen, you...

00:15:38.139 --> 00:15:41.220
From today, I'll be obedient.

00:15:42.279 --> 00:15:43.220
I'll do as you said.

00:15:44.340 --> 00:15:45.580
Take good care of myself.

00:15:52.399 --> 00:15:53.220
Let's eat.

00:15:54.139 --> 00:15:54.720
Here.

00:15:56.340 --> 00:15:57.399
Have fried dough.

00:15:58.120 --> 00:16:00.360
Qianqian loves this pickled vegetable.

00:16:02.980 --> 00:16:04.000
You mixed it yourself?

00:16:04.000 --> 00:16:04.899
I mixed it myself.

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:10.100
Mom.

00:16:10.840 --> 00:16:12.600
Look at this watch Dad has, is it nice?

00:16:13.899 --> 00:16:14.899
Why touched that?

00:16:14.899 --> 00:16:16.399
This is valuable. Put it back.

00:16:19.720 --> 00:16:20.340
Dad.

00:16:21.639 --> 00:16:23.240
Why don't you come home often?

00:16:24.720 --> 00:16:26.139
I have a lot of things to handle.

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:31.759
Dad, where are you going?

00:16:32.360 --> 00:16:33.159
Going upstairs.

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:35.700
You... It's time to eat.

00:16:36.899 --> 00:16:38.879
You eat first. I'll eat later.

00:16:39.000 --> 00:16:39.740
Wait!

00:16:41.860 --> 00:16:43.720
Want to go upstairs? Get past me first.

00:16:45.879 --> 00:16:46.720
You brat.

00:16:49.360 --> 00:16:50.259
Be serious.

00:16:51.779 --> 00:16:52.340
Come.

00:16:54.659 --> 00:16:55.159
Come.

00:16:59.519 --> 00:17:00.340
I won.

00:17:02.220 --> 00:17:02.759
Go eat.

00:17:08.579 --> 00:17:10.160
Look at the watch Mom bought for you.

00:17:12.579 --> 00:17:13.140
Is it nice?

00:17:18.339 --> 00:17:19.220
I'll put it on you.

00:17:22.460 --> 00:17:25.000
Xiaoliang, come help me
with the chopsticks.

00:17:25.339 --> 00:17:27.279
Mom, look at Dad's watch. Is it nice?

00:17:29.220 --> 00:17:29.980
Yes.

00:17:39.519 --> 00:17:40.319
Guangcai.

00:17:42.140 --> 00:17:45.839
Sooner or later,
I'll tell you everything.

00:17:48.980 --> 00:17:49.579
I'm waiting.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:17:59.799
It's so nice for us to eat together.

00:18:02.700 --> 00:18:03.759
This is your home.

00:18:04.339 --> 00:18:07.799
Eating together with Dad and Mom

00:18:08.039 --> 00:18:09.240
makes you that happy?

00:18:10.180 --> 00:18:11.000
Just eat.

00:18:14.400 --> 00:18:15.759
You love fried chicken, right?

00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:17.140
This one is lean.

00:18:17.140 --> 00:18:17.779
Eat it.

00:18:19.200 --> 00:18:20.180
Thanks, Dad.

00:18:20.826 --> 00:18:24.058
(Beiyan No. 2 Middle School)

00:18:35.700 --> 00:18:36.259
Zhu.

00:18:38.819 --> 00:18:40.700
Hello, everyone.

00:18:41.539 --> 00:18:43.339
(Parents' Meeting)
Thanks for taking the time

00:18:43.339 --> 00:18:46.000
to attend the parents' meeting.

00:18:46.740 --> 00:18:49.799
As you all know, this semester
is the second semester of grade eight.

00:18:50.460 --> 00:18:52.279
The high school
entrance exam is coming up.

00:18:52.279 --> 00:18:55.339
This is crucial for
both students and parents.

00:18:55.720 --> 00:19:00.539
We hope you could cooperate with us
to complete this semester's tasks.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:03.740
(Beiyan No.2 Middle School)
I didn't expect you'd come.

00:19:05.140 --> 00:19:07.819
Zhu, last time you
went to the company...

00:19:09.519 --> 00:19:10.720
We haven't seen in a while.

00:19:11.440 --> 00:19:12.759
Have you been quite busy?

00:19:14.460 --> 00:19:17.819
How about finding a time
to get together someday?

00:19:18.140 --> 00:19:18.920
No need.

00:19:19.839 --> 00:19:23.299
The people you meet are all big shots
who can help you make money.

00:19:23.740 --> 00:19:26.740
I am not a big shot. No need to force
yourself to get together with me.

00:19:28.640 --> 00:19:31.460
Zhu, you make it
sound like we're strangers.

00:19:32.039 --> 00:19:33.759
You're a celebrity in Beiyan.

00:19:34.180 --> 00:19:38.000
I'm just curious to know why you have
suddenly kept such a low profile lately,

00:19:39.539 --> 00:19:42.059
without public appearances
or interviews?

00:19:42.839 --> 00:19:44.544
Why have you suddenly
kept a low profile?

00:19:48.220 --> 00:19:51.000
I'm tired. I want some peace.

00:19:52.000 --> 00:19:54.460
I let the subordinates handle the work.

00:19:56.259 --> 00:19:58.299
One has to take the blame
for what they've done.

00:19:58.980 --> 00:20:02.200
It's not like you can just have peace
whenever you want.

00:20:17.299 --> 00:20:17.940
Oranges.

00:20:22.700 --> 00:20:24.940
Please hurry up. I've got things to do.

00:20:24.940 --> 00:20:25.579
Just a moment.

00:20:25.579 --> 00:20:26.420
Let me.

00:20:26.640 --> 00:20:28.220
Sorry, let me handle it.

00:20:29.839 --> 00:20:30.579
Two fifty.

00:20:31.420 --> 00:20:32.220
Here, take it.

00:20:32.299 --> 00:20:33.000
Thanks.

00:20:33.299 --> 00:20:34.299
Take care, come again.

00:20:35.200 --> 00:20:36.799
I'm still not very good at using this.

00:20:37.000 --> 00:20:38.400
I'll practice more.

00:20:38.400 --> 00:20:40.000
It's okay, you've only
been here for a week.

00:20:40.000 --> 00:20:42.420
Too many things to handle.
You'll get the hang of it.

00:20:42.640 --> 00:20:43.339
- Got it.
- It's okay.

00:20:43.819 --> 00:20:44.319
Go ahead.

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:49.400
Xiaoliang! Take her and go.

00:20:50.140 --> 00:20:51.240
(Rongfa Noodle Shop)
I'm going back, Mr. Chen.

00:20:52.299 --> 00:20:53.079
Hurry up.

00:20:53.940 --> 00:20:54.480
Hurry!

00:20:54.480 --> 00:20:55.720
Sit in the back, you two, okay?

00:20:56.940 --> 00:20:57.700
Drive carefully.

00:20:57.700 --> 00:20:58.500
Okay, I know.

00:21:01.420 --> 00:21:04.559
Zhu, I saw Qianqian came back
with Meng Guangcai.

00:21:04.740 --> 00:21:05.920
Didn't you pick up Qianqian?

00:21:06.304 --> 00:21:08.178
(Huifen)

00:21:16.954 --> 00:21:23.290
(Telephone directory, Xue Qin)

00:21:37.440 --> 00:21:38.480
This color is stylish.

00:21:40.539 --> 00:21:41.259
Zhu.

00:21:41.319 --> 00:21:42.299
Zhu.

00:21:42.900 --> 00:21:44.819
We were taking Xiaoliang
to the amusement park.

00:21:44.819 --> 00:21:46.940
Xiaoliang said he wanted
to come find Qianqian to go.

00:21:47.740 --> 00:21:48.960
They had a great time today.

00:21:49.319 --> 00:21:51.640
Qianqian, why don't you tell
your dad where you went?

00:21:52.440 --> 00:21:54.519
Dad, we had so much fun
at the amusement park.

00:21:54.519 --> 00:21:55.799
And we had fast food.

00:21:55.799 --> 00:21:59.279
This. Uncle bought this toy for me.

00:21:59.440 --> 00:22:01.200
And there were lots of snacks.

00:22:01.200 --> 00:22:04.039
I said I couldn't accept it,
but Auntie bought it for me anyway.

00:22:04.299 --> 00:22:05.140
I'm glad you like it.

00:22:05.720 --> 00:22:09.559
Zhu, why are you still working in that
cafeteria? It's a waste of your talent.

00:22:09.920 --> 00:22:12.539
You could just quit. It's fine
if you do not work in my company.

00:22:13.019 --> 00:22:15.539
See what you want to do,
and tell me if you have any ideas.

00:22:16.039 --> 00:22:16.980
I'm here for you.

00:22:17.079 --> 00:22:17.700
Exactly.

00:22:17.819 --> 00:22:18.660
My turn, right?

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:31.039
Huifen, back when
Caisheng Group was first founded,

00:22:31.140 --> 00:22:33.039
it was all thanks
to Zhu helping Guangcai.

00:22:33.759 --> 00:22:35.579
Otherwise, our family
wouldn't be like this.

00:22:35.920 --> 00:22:39.779
Back then, Guangcai said to buy
an apartment for you in this complex,

00:22:40.839 --> 00:22:42.740
so we picked one out for you.

00:22:42.900 --> 00:22:44.319
I wonder if you like it.

00:22:44.319 --> 00:22:45.000
I cannot take it.

00:22:45.000 --> 00:22:46.339
Wait, Xue Qin, I can't...

00:22:46.339 --> 00:22:47.339
- I can't take it.
- Take a look.

00:22:47.339 --> 00:22:48.339
No, we...

00:22:48.339 --> 00:22:49.240
We can't accept this.

00:22:49.240 --> 00:22:50.279
Xue Qin, take it back.

00:22:50.279 --> 00:22:51.440
Take all the things away.

00:22:52.420 --> 00:22:53.480
Take them away.

00:22:54.539 --> 00:22:55.200
Go.

00:22:56.539 --> 00:22:57.200
Take them away.

00:23:00.059 --> 00:23:00.799
Get out now!

00:23:07.299 --> 00:23:09.039
Huifen, we're leaving now.

00:23:09.500 --> 00:23:10.519
Don't scare the children.

00:23:10.799 --> 00:23:11.319
We're going.

00:23:11.319 --> 00:23:12.180
We're going then.

00:23:12.180 --> 00:23:12.920
Sorry about that.

00:23:15.660 --> 00:23:16.240
Give it to me.

00:23:42.160 --> 00:23:42.799
Dad!

00:23:42.799 --> 00:23:44.019
- Dad!
- Zhu!

00:23:44.019 --> 00:23:44.640
Zhu!

00:23:45.220 --> 00:23:45.799
Zhu!

00:23:46.039 --> 00:23:47.259
Zhu, are you okay? Zhu!

00:23:47.259 --> 00:23:47.940
Dad!

00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:48.579
Zhu!

00:23:50.842 --> 00:23:56.154
(One month later)

00:23:59.079 --> 00:24:02.259
Finally home. The weather's
changed, it's getting cold.

00:24:04.319 --> 00:24:05.720
It's best to be home.

00:24:27.079 --> 00:24:28.079
What are these?

00:24:29.460 --> 00:24:32.940
While you were in the hospital,
Liu Hua came several times.

00:24:33.539 --> 00:24:35.460
He just stood at the door
without coming in.

00:24:36.440 --> 00:24:38.019
It made me feel quite upset.

00:24:39.259 --> 00:24:40.920
I know this case means
everything to you.

00:24:41.940 --> 00:24:43.039
If I stop you from it,

00:24:44.480 --> 00:24:45.700
I'm afraid you'd collapse.

00:24:49.140 --> 00:24:50.039
Then investigate it

00:24:51.059 --> 00:24:52.140
thoroughly,

00:24:52.920 --> 00:24:54.079
to avenge Qianqian's father.

00:24:56.000 --> 00:24:58.220
If the police station won't let you,
do it at home.

00:24:59.440 --> 00:25:00.339
I support you.

00:25:02.460 --> 00:25:04.140
But there's one thing, Zhu.

00:25:04.700 --> 00:25:07.039
You can investigate,
but your health still comes first.

00:25:09.579 --> 00:25:11.700
You have to quit smoking and drinking.

00:25:12.500 --> 00:25:15.200
Manage your emotions.
Don't get agitated.

00:25:17.640 --> 00:25:19.019
You have to live well.

00:25:20.519 --> 00:25:23.500
You have to watch Qianqian grow up

00:25:24.299 --> 00:25:25.220
and get married.

00:25:26.839 --> 00:25:28.256
We have to see our grandchildren.

00:25:29.519 --> 00:25:30.299
Right?

00:26:06.700 --> 00:26:08.259
I've told you everything I know.

00:26:10.299 --> 00:26:12.299
Don't you have
other cases to investigate?

00:26:13.720 --> 00:26:14.579
Just chatting.

00:26:16.140 --> 00:26:17.920
Enough about the robbery case.

00:26:19.460 --> 00:26:20.759
Let's talk about Zuo Long.

00:26:26.680 --> 00:26:28.160
I have nothing to say about Zuo Long.

00:26:28.640 --> 00:26:29.299
Not familiar.

00:26:30.220 --> 00:26:31.220
How about Xue Qin?

00:26:32.799 --> 00:26:34.079
Familiar with Xue Qin, right?

00:26:38.200 --> 00:26:39.660
Zuo Long raped Xue Qin.

00:26:41.920 --> 00:26:42.700
Did you know that?

00:26:47.279 --> 00:26:49.319
Caisheng Group has plenty of rumors.

00:26:50.579 --> 00:26:51.960
I heard something much crazier.

00:26:53.200 --> 00:26:54.259
Does it concern me?

00:26:55.039 --> 00:26:57.960
Does it concern you?
Does it concern the case?

00:27:02.579 --> 00:27:05.079
Let me go back. I need rest.

00:27:33.299 --> 00:27:34.259
Yonghui,

00:27:37.700 --> 00:27:38.940
he came to my place.

00:27:56.180 --> 00:27:56.960
67.

00:27:58.680 --> 00:27:59.460
68.

00:28:00.940 --> 00:28:01.720
69.

00:28:03.200 --> 00:28:04.000
70.

00:28:05.500 --> 00:28:06.339
71.

00:28:15.539 --> 00:28:16.339
72.

00:28:24.634 --> 00:28:27.920
(Police)

00:28:27.920 --> 00:28:30.339
Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu's
test results are out.

00:28:30.839 --> 00:28:32.259
(Test results)
They don't match the DNA at the scene.

00:28:32.579 --> 00:28:35.259
Jiao Lijun is also not
Meng Xiaoliang's biological father.

00:28:39.700 --> 00:28:41.000
What about Ma Zhongwu?

00:28:42.000 --> 00:28:43.920
Ma Zhongwu's DNA doesn't match either.

00:28:44.140 --> 00:28:46.299
He can't answer
any details about the case.

00:28:46.579 --> 00:28:49.940
He's just delaying his execution
by talking nonsense nonstop.

00:28:50.299 --> 00:28:53.960
I think we can basically
rule him out as a suspect.

00:28:54.700 --> 00:28:55.539
So that means,

00:28:55.799 --> 00:28:59.140
before Jiao Lijun surrendered,
he didn't know we had found Ma Zhongwu.

00:28:59.339 --> 00:29:02.299
That's why he insisted
Ma Zhongwu was involved in the robbery.

00:29:02.960 --> 00:29:04.460
If that's the case,

00:29:04.700 --> 00:29:08.019
their plan of using Ma Zhongwu
as a substitute for Meng Guangcai

00:29:08.460 --> 00:29:09.799
has already failed.

00:29:10.799 --> 00:29:11.799
Which means,

00:29:13.200 --> 00:29:14.519
the four robbers are

00:29:15.079 --> 00:29:18.000
Meng, Wang, Jiao, and Zuo Long, right?

00:29:18.339 --> 00:29:20.500
We can't confirm Zuo Long yet.

00:29:20.799 --> 00:29:23.460
And we can't confirm

00:29:24.920 --> 00:29:25.920
Meng Guangcai either.

00:29:37.259 --> 00:29:40.500
Guys, we only have
these last few days left.

00:29:41.960 --> 00:29:43.960
If we still can't offer solid evidence,

00:29:44.299 --> 00:29:46.700
it's very likely Meng Guangcai
will be acquitted of a charge.

00:29:47.200 --> 00:29:48.500
Then we'll be on the defensive.

00:29:49.079 --> 00:29:51.039
Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu

00:29:52.079 --> 00:29:53.759
are just pawns.

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:58.299
We still need to focus on
the player, Meng Guangcai.

00:29:59.299 --> 00:30:01.759
What do you mean, Zhu?

00:30:02.700 --> 00:30:03.559
Same old routine?

00:30:07.579 --> 00:30:08.420
Show the evidence.

00:30:09.200 --> 00:30:11.900
Show him the evidence.
Show him the test results.

00:30:12.019 --> 00:30:15.039
Meng Guangcai has always
reacted strangely about his son, right?

00:30:15.039 --> 00:30:16.420
Good. Show him the evidence

00:30:16.420 --> 00:30:18.299
and see his reaction.
Let's see if he knows

00:30:18.299 --> 00:30:21.140
who his son's
biological father really is.

00:30:24.519 --> 00:30:25.220
Agreed.

00:30:26.079 --> 00:30:28.700
You know Meng Xiaoliang
isn't your biological son, right?

00:30:34.299 --> 00:30:35.839
I don't understand what you mean.

00:30:37.839 --> 00:30:39.579
Xiaoliang is definitely
my biological son.

00:30:39.960 --> 00:30:41.579
Meng Xiaoliang is Jiao Lijun's son.

00:30:43.680 --> 00:30:47.200
Captain Li's learned some tricks.
This lie sounds so real.

00:30:50.200 --> 00:30:51.039
Meng Xiaoliang

00:30:52.539 --> 00:30:54.519
is Jiao Lijun's biological son.

00:30:55.920 --> 00:30:57.299
Is that the answer in your mind?

00:31:08.500 --> 00:31:09.240
Pay attention.

00:31:11.460 --> 00:31:12.519
It's a critical moment.

00:31:17.940 --> 00:31:19.180
Xiaoliang is my son.

00:31:22.299 --> 00:31:25.920
Don't lie to me. Don't try
to trick me into talking.

00:31:33.460 --> 00:31:36.140
Read it. I'm tired of beating
around the bush with you.

00:31:37.759 --> 00:31:38.420
Read it.

00:31:54.080 --> 00:31:56.410
(Probability of paternal match: 0.9999%)

00:32:13.519 --> 00:32:14.940
That's exactly the right reaction.

00:32:15.839 --> 00:32:17.259
He really doesn't know about it.

00:32:19.299 --> 00:32:20.140
So?

00:32:22.500 --> 00:32:23.500
Have you read it clearly?

00:32:31.000 --> 00:32:33.299
Tell me what you think.

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:36.259
Nothing.

00:32:39.259 --> 00:32:40.500
Xue Qin told us,

00:32:41.500 --> 00:32:43.259
she was once raped.

00:32:44.460 --> 00:32:45.940
From what we know now,

00:32:45.940 --> 00:32:51.000
the rapist was involved in the 6.10 case
along with Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu.

00:32:51.779 --> 00:32:52.960
Is this person Zuo Long?

00:32:58.079 --> 00:32:59.299
I wasn't involved.

00:33:00.500 --> 00:33:01.700
I don't know.

00:33:04.259 --> 00:33:07.759
Don't try to trick me
with these fake reports.

00:33:08.339 --> 00:33:10.019
I won't believe a single word.

00:33:21.242 --> 00:33:22.720
(Gubei Province Biological Identification
Research Center, Test Report)

00:33:26.519 --> 00:33:30.640
You know very well
whether this report is real or fake.

00:33:31.000 --> 00:33:32.039
So I suggest you

00:33:34.039 --> 00:33:35.420
to think it over.

00:33:54.420 --> 00:33:55.960
I've raised another man's son.

00:33:56.759 --> 00:33:57.759
It's eating me up inside.

00:34:04.519 --> 00:34:07.299
- Is Meng Xiaoliang your son?
- He...

00:34:09.300 --> 00:34:10.199
What?

00:34:11.760 --> 00:34:14.960
He's not your son? Then whose son is he?

00:34:15.400 --> 00:34:17.920
Tell me, and I'll kill him right away.

00:34:25.420 --> 00:34:26.619
(Xue Qin told us,)

00:34:27.539 --> 00:34:29.420
(she was once raped.)

00:34:31.320 --> 00:34:32.119
Guangcai.

00:34:33.920 --> 00:34:37.679
Sooner or later,
I'll tell you everything.

00:34:57.079 --> 00:34:59.079
Meng Xiaoliang
had a medical check-up recently.

00:34:59.780 --> 00:35:02.500
His test results were compared
to the blood sample left

00:35:02.500 --> 00:35:05.360
by a suspect
at the crime scene of 6.10 case.

00:35:05.579 --> 00:35:07.904
The two blood samples
indicate a father-son relationship.

00:35:17.039 --> 00:35:22.420
Meng Guangcai refuses
to answer all our questions.

00:35:22.980 --> 00:35:26.579
Is Zuo Long really
Meng Xiaoliang's biological father?

00:35:29.360 --> 00:35:31.480
Why has it hit Meng Guangcai so hard?

00:35:32.219 --> 00:35:34.019
The probing did have some effect,

00:35:34.480 --> 00:35:38.500
but we're running out of time.

00:35:38.800 --> 00:35:41.199
If Meng Guangcai keeps
holding out like this,

00:35:41.539 --> 00:35:43.440
we can just watch him walk out.

00:35:44.119 --> 00:35:45.719
That mysterious person at the cemetery

00:35:46.760 --> 00:35:48.000
appeared

00:35:48.000 --> 00:35:50.719
precisely when Meng Guangcai
was under investigation.

00:35:51.320 --> 00:35:52.300
There must be a reason.

00:35:53.079 --> 00:35:53.920
He did it on purpose?

00:35:54.500 --> 00:35:55.320
Exactly.

00:35:56.119 --> 00:35:57.960
Maybe he's trying to make us

00:35:58.480 --> 00:36:00.800
see but not get close to him,

00:36:02.500 --> 00:36:04.579
or even covering for Meng Guangcai.

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:06.940
I'll make a bold guess.

00:36:07.300 --> 00:36:10.340
Zuo Long might be hiding his identity
and still active out there.

00:36:11.260 --> 00:36:13.000
That mysterious person might be him.

00:36:53.500 --> 00:36:58.524
=The Silent Rift=